VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT roleRef\s*:[^}]*name\s*:\s*cluster-admin
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:cluster-admin && MISSING:# intentional|# required|system:|kube-system|namespace:\s*kube
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects ClusterRoleBindings that grant the cluster-admin role to subjects.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for ClusterRoleBinding to cluster-admin.
